Config.Description:
&lt;b&gt;empty&lt;/b&gt; =&gt; SSL disabled &lt;b&gt; (NOT recommended)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt; 
&lt;b&gt;letsencrypt&lt;/b&gt; =&gt; Enables Let's Encrypt certificates &lt;b&gt; (/etc/letsencrypt/live/example.com/) &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;custom&lt;/b&gt; =&gt; Enables custom certificates &lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;manual&lt;/b&gt; =&gt; Let's you manually specify locations of your SSL certificates for non-standard cases &lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;self-signed&lt;/b&gt;=&gt; Enables self-signed certificates

&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; If &lt;b&gt;emtpy&lt;/b&gt; is &lt;b&gt; not &lt;/b&gt; choosen, go to =&gt; Show more settings...
